#. translators: 1: artist name, 2: site name, 3: proposed cap, 4: closing date
#: includes/Artist/CommunityCapNotification.php:60
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Hi %1$s,\n"
"\n"
"The %2$s community has opened a vote to change the membership size cap to "
"%3$s. The vote closes on %4$s.\n"
"\n"
"A strict majority of active members (more than 50%%) must vote yes for the "
"new cap to be adopted. Sign in to your account to cast your vote.\n"
"\n"
"— %2$s"
msgstr ""
"Bonjour %1$s,\n"
"\n"
"La communauté %2$s a ouvert un vote pour modifier le plafond de taille "
"d’adhésion à %3$s. Le vote se clôture le %4$s.\n"
"\n"
"Une majorité simple des membres actifs (plus de 50%%) doit voter oui pour "
"que le nouveau plafond soit adopté. Connectez-vous à votre compte pour voter."
"\n"
"\n"
"— %2$s"

#. translators: 1: voter display name, 2: site name, 3: closing date, 4: yes URL, 5: no URL
#: includes/Artist/DepartureNotification.php:311
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Hi %1$s,\n"
"\n"
"The %2$s community has opened a vote to remove a member. The vote closes on "
"%3$s.\n"
"\n"
"Cast your vote:\n"
"\n"
"Vote YES (remove): %4$s\n"
"\n"
"Vote NO (keep):    %5$s\n"
"\n"
"A majority of active members (more than 50%%) must vote yes for the removal "
"to proceed. You can change your vote by clicking the other link before the "
"deadline.\n"
"\n"
"— %2$s"
msgstr ""
"Bonjour %1$s,\n"
"\n"
"La communauté %2$s a ouvert un vote pour révoquer un membre. Le vote se "
"termine le %3$s.\n"
"\n"
"Exprimez votre vote :\n"
"\n"
"Vote OUI (révoquer) : %4$s\n"
"\n"
"Vote NON (conserver) :    %5$s\n"
"\n"
"Une majorité des membres actifs (plus de 50%%) doit voter oui pour que la "
"révocation puisse avoir lieu. Vous pouvez modifier votre vote en cliquant "
"sur l’autre lien avant la date limite.\n"
"\n"
"— %2$s"

#. translators: 1: artist display name, 2: site name, 3: confirmation URL
#: includes/Artist/DepartureNotification.php:73
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Hi %1$s,\n"
"\n"
"We received a request to remove your account and all your published work "
"from %2$s.\n"
"\n"
"If you made this request, click the link below to confirm. This action is "
"permanent and cannot be undone.\n"
"\n"
"%3$s\n"
"\n"
"If you did not make this request, you can ignore this email — your account "
"remains unchanged.\n"
"\n"
"— %2$s"
msgstr ""
"Bonjour %1$s,\n"
"\n"
"Nous avons reçu une demande de suppression de votre compte et de toutes vos "
"œuvres publiées de %2$s.\n"
"\n"
"Si vous êtes à l’origine de cette demande, cliquez sur le lien ci-dessous "
"pour confirmer. Cette action est définitive et ne peut pas être annulée.\n"
"\n"
"%3$s\n"
"\n"
"Si vous n’êtes pas à l’origine de cette demande, vous pouvez ignorer cet e-"
"mail — votre compte reste inchangé.\n"
"\n"
"— %2$s"

